      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has some fading in the clear coat and a few minor parking lot dings, while the interior shows typical wear on the driver's seat and carpet. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone looking for reliable transportation without the premium price of a showroom model.",
