      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. With a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original luster, this motorcar offers an ownership experience indistinguishable from new. We invite serious inquiries for this masterfully preserved example of engineering excellence.",
