      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. I\u2019ve treated this car like my absolute baby\u2014it\u2019s in pristine, showroom condition with not a single scratch or dent to be found! It drives like a total dream and honestly still has that fresh new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
