    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint with a mirror-like finish, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather seats are supple with no visible wear on the bolsters, and the original 'new car' scent is still subtly present. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive folder of maintenance records included. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never been driven in inclement weather. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
